  skullRemark: "Hehe, tricky one to judge, huh?"
  luciferRemark: "Money and life \u2014 shall we weigh them on the same moral scale?\r\n\r\n(Pause.)\r\n\r\nThree lives saved. One life lost to greed. What\u2019s the exchange rate?\r\n\r\nHe had a chance to be something better. For one brief moment, he was. And then...\r\n\r\n(Soft laugh.)\r\n\r\nOld habits."
